headline: BofA (BAC) Q4 2025 Earnings Call Transcript
summary: Thank you for joining us to review our fourth quarter results.  During the quarter, we elected to change the accounting method related to our tax-related equity investments in order to better align our financial statement presentation with the economic and financial impact of those investments.  The primary impact of the accounting change was a reclassification between the income statement line items in our income statement, which had an insignificant impact on net income.

content.title: BofA (BAC) Q4 2025 Earnings Call Transcript
content.summary: Thank you for joining us to review our fourth quarter results.  During the quarter, we elected to change the accounting method related to our tax-related equity investments in order to better align our financial statement presentation with the economic and financial impact of those investments.  The primary impact of the accounting change was a reclassification between the income statement line items in our income statement, which had an insignificant impact on net income.
